quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  20,55,Kuwona (umhlaba) sanidala futhi siyoniphindisela kuwona futhi siyonivusa kuwona ngesinye isikhathi
  20,56,Futhi ngempela samkhombisa zonke izimpawu zethu (uFaro) kepha waphika futhi wenqaba
  20,57,"(UFaro) wathi, “ngakube uze kuthina ukuze usikhiphe ezweni lethu ngomlingo wakho Oh Mose!?”"
  20,58,"Ngakho-ke ngempela nathi sizokulethela umlingo ofana nawo, ngakho-ke nquma isikhathi (sokuhlangana) phakathi kwethu nawe ungehluleki ukusigcina, thina nawe siyobe siseshashalazini"
  20,59,"(UMose) wathi, “isikhathi senu esinqunyiwe ingosuku lomkhosi futhi abantu bayobe behlangene ndawonye ngezikhathi zasekuseni”"
  20,60,Ngakho-ke uFaro wahamba wayesehlanganisa icebo lakhe wayeseyeza (kuMose)
  20,61,UMose wathi kubona (kubalumbi bakaFaro) “usizi kunina ningamqambeli uMvelinqangi amanga hleze anibhubhise ngesijeziso futhi angeke aphumelele lowo oqamba (amanga)”
  20,62,Ngakho-ke kwaba khona ukuphikisana phakathi kwabo ngodaba lwabo futhi bayigcina iyimfihlo inkulumo yangasese
  20,63,Bathi (abantu bakaFaro) “laba bobabili (uMose no-Aroni) ngempela bangabalumbi bobabili bafuna ukunigxosha ezweni lenu ngomlingo wabo futhi banikhiphe endleleni yenu eyisibonelo”
  20,64,Ngakho-ke hlanganisani icebo lenu bese niza ningudwendwe futhi uzobe ulehlulile lolusuku lowo ozonqoba
  20,65,"Bathi, “Oh Mose! Uzophonsa noma sizokuba ngabokuqala ukuphonsa na?”"
  20,66,"(UMose) wathi, “qha phonsani nina phansi, kwaba ilapho izintambo zabo kanye nezinduku zabo zibukeka sengathi ziza kuyena zigijima ngenxa yomlingo wabo”"
  20,67,Ngakho-ke uMose wazizwa enokwesaba
  20,68,"Sathi, “ungesabi ngempela nguwena ongaphezulu omkhulu”"
  20,69,"Futhi phonsa phansi lokho okusesandleni sakho sokudla kuzogwinya lokho abakwenzile, kuphela abakwenzile kuyicebo lomlumbi futhi angeke aphumelele umlumbi ngisho noma ngabe uqhamukaphi"
  20,70,"Ngakho-ke bawa phansi abalumbi bakhothama bathi, “siyakholwa eNkosini ka-Aroni noMose”"
  20,71,"(UFaro) wathi (kubalumbi bakhe), “nikholwe kuye ngaphambi kokuba ngininike imvume na? Ngempela yena ungumholi wenu onifundise umlingo ngakho-ke ngempela ngizoninquma izandlazenukanyenezinyawozenuezinhlangothiniezehlukene futhi ngempela ngizoninqamuleza eziqwini zemithi yesundu futhi ngempela nizokwazi ukuthi ngubani phakathi kwethu onzima ekujeziseni okubeleselayo”"
  20,72,"Bathi (abalumbi bakaFaro), “Asisoze sikhethe wena ngaphezu kwalokho osekufikile kuthina okuyizimpawu ezicacile (nangaphezu) kwalowo owasidalayo ngakho-ke yehlulela njengoba uthanda ukwehlulela, kuphela wehlulela kulempilo yalomhlaba”"
  20,73,Ngempela sikholiwe eNkosini yethu ukuze isithethelele amaphutha ethu kanye nakulokho osiphoqelele kukona okungumlingo futhi uMvelinqangi ungcono futhi ukhona ngasosonke isikhathi
  20,74,"Ngempela lowo ozayo eNkosini yakhe eyisoni, ngakho-ke ngempela okwakhe yisihogo angeke aze afe kusona futhi angeke aze aphile"
  20,75,Futhi lowo ozayo kuyona (iNkosi yakhe) eyikholwa futhi enza izenzo ezinhle ezilungileyo ngakho-ke labo okwabo amazinga aphakeme
  20,76,Izivande zaphakade okugeleza ngaphansi kwazo imifula bayohlala khona ingunaphakade futhi lokho kungumvuzo walabo abazihlambululayo
  20,77,"Futhi ngempela sakwembula kuMose ukuthi makahambe ebusuku nezinceku zami ngakho-ke bashayele indlela eyomile olwandle, ungesabi ukuficwa (ngamabutho kaFaro) futhi ungesabi (ukuminza olwandle)"
  20,78,"Ngakho-ke uFaro wabalandela kanye namabutho akhe, kepha ulwandle lwabagalela futhi lwabamboza"
  20,79,Futhi uFaro wabadukisa abantu bakhe futhi wangabaholeli (endleleni eqondile)
  20,80,Oh bantwana bakwa-Israyeli! Ngempela sanisindisa esitheni senu futhi senza isethembiso nani ehlangothini langakwesokudla lwentaba futhi sanehlisela phansi imana kanye nezigcwaca
  20,81,"Dlanini ezintweni ezinhle lokho esanabela kona futhi ningabi abangahloniphi kulokho, hleze intukuthelo yami yehlele phezu kwenu futhi noma ngabe ubani eyehlela phezu kwakhe intukuthelo yami ngempela ubhubhile"
  20,82,Futhi ngempela mina ngiyathethelela noma ngabe ubani ozisolayo futhi akholwe enze nokuhle okulungileyo bese ehamba endleleni elungileyo